{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a couple of bridges over that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of them had already been blown off, and there was only one left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, um, that's where we thought, well, um, there's only one thing what we have to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's just a split second reaction again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said to my wife, OK, after this-- what happened, I have to go and see and come to the other side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was then on the 9th-- 9th, on a Monday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a pass for Kamp Westerbork to enter it myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to-- to Westerbork, because I knew that Westerbork itself was already liberated at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew that [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ivan ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Brits ?] was still in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a German soldier watching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, can I get across?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, uh, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I showed my pass for Kamp Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, well, that must be a good one, then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hey, he's on our side, he works there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he told me that I had killed just a boy of 17 years of age on the other side for treason.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] For treason to attempt, not to [? assassinate. ?] When I went on the road further towards the, uh, township, there were farmers on the side we-- uh, whom we knew.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said to me, Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Van As, don't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are shooting there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, shooting?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, why?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, well, they are still fighting around it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, well, have they collected your milk this morning for the, uh, pasteurization of the milk?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Said, yeah, he went over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, well, if he can go, I can go, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
